{"tid":2241300,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★調查﹕內地億萬富豪增至415人！！！","createTime":"2020-10-13T08:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T10:47:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b631fb90bb0aa68a4cf0e143ce2af24182a98aea","tid":2241300,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"瑞銀及羅兵咸永道發表《2020年瑞銀/羅兵咸永道億萬富豪報告》，報告指出今年4月至7月間，億萬富豪的財富出現強勁增長，其中亞太區億萬富豪財富增長36%至3.3萬億美元，增幅遠超歐洲、中東及非洲地區和美洲地區。<br />\n<br />\n亞太區億萬富豪財富增長強勁，主要由中國內地富豪所推動。截至2020年7月底<span class=\"xx-large\">中國內地億萬富豪數目，破紀錄增至415人</span>，總財富達1.7萬億美元。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201007/390506458946605056.jpeg/3K1HWAS5d3oyYeFBkqxL5h7Ow3tm2XeE0RrBjNEawYw?v=w1280r16_9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201007%2F390506458946605056.jpeg%2F3K1HWAS5d3oyYeFBkqxL5h7Ow3tm2XeE0RrBjNEawYw%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=c287e1a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201007/390506458946605056.jpeg/3K1HWAS5d3oyYeFBkqxL5h7Ow3tm2XeE0RrBjNEawYw?v=w1280r16_9</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/532738/%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%84%84%E8%90%AC%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3415%E4%BA%BA-%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80-%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E8%80%85-%E7%96%AB-%E5%B8%82%E6%88%90%E8%B4%8F%E5%AE%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F532738%2F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25A2%259E%25E8%2587%25B3415%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%2591%259E%25E9%258A%2580-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2580%2585-%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25B4%258F%25E5%25AE%25B6&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=1d